items.content_text: Initially thought this was a young Morethia boulengeri but it did not have a reddish tail and on closer inspection had four fingers and five toes while Morethia have 5 digits on all limbs. Acacia leprosa s.l., Peltoschema orphana

Fireblight Beetle on Acacia leprosa. Interesting observation as it is generally considered to feed exclusively on Acacia dealbata and Acacia mearnsii.
Observation by David Wakefield.
